{[#] White's queen is awkwardly placed. Can Black benefit from that?} 8... d5
$1 $146 {Black's best move.} 9. Nxd5 (9. exd5 $2 {is a blunder and after} Nb4
10. Qd2 Bf5 $19 {[%csl Rc2] White cannot protect the c2-pawn.}) 9... Nxd5 10.
