{[#] How should Black continue here?} 10... Bxf5 $1 $146 {A very strong
novelty. Black sacrifices a piece to benefit from the uncastled king and open
the center. This excellent idea gives Black a big advantage.} 11. exf5 d5 {
[%cal Ge5e4] Black is threatening to play ...e4.} 12. Nxe5 Rfe8 13. Kf1 Bd6 14.
Qf2 Qxf2+ 15. Kxf2 Nxe5 $17 {The position is clearly better for Black.} *

