{[#] Black's rook is under attack. After a retreat to a8 or a6 White will play
g4-g5 with a clear advantage. But again Black has a fantastic resource. How
can he continue his attack without losing a tempo?} 15... b5 $3 $146 {[%cal
Gc8b7] This is a very powerful and original exchange sacrifice. Instead of
losing time with a rook move, Black prepares ... Bb7 immediately.} (15... Ra8
$2 16. g4 $16 {[%cal Gg4g5]}) (15... Ra6 $2 16. g4 $16 {[%cal Gg4g5]}) 16. Nxa4
(16. Nxb5 $2 {is not possible and after} Nxe4 $19 {White's position is
collapsing.}) 16... bxa4 17. Nd2 a3 $40 {[%csl Rc1] Black has a very dangerous
attack.} *

